*FvwmButtons(Padding 0 2, Icon terminal.xpm, Action 'Exec "xterm" xterm &')
*FvwmButtons(Padding 0 2, Icon lock.xpm, Action 'Exec "xlock" xlock')
*FvwmButtons(Padding 0 2, Icon restart.xpm, Action Restart)
*FvwmButtons(End)

